<div class="card">
    <div class="card-header border-bottom">
        <h4 class="card-title">Notifications</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body pt-2" id="noti-details">
        <h5 class="mb-0">
            알림에 관해서 설정하세요 <strong>추후 모바일로도 알림 지원 예정입니다.</strong>
        </h5>
    </div>
    <div class="table-responsive">
        <table class="table text-nowrap text-center border-bottom">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th class="text-start">Type</th>
                    <th>✉️ Email</th>
                    <th>👩🏻‍💻 App</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td class="text-start">광고 / 홍보</td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="form-check d-flex justify-content-center">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="adNotiEmail">
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="form-check d-flex justify-content-center">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="adNotiApp">
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="text-start">Jobcast 구인 정보</td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="form-check d-flex justify-content-center">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="jobcastNotiEmail">
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="form-check d-flex justify-content-center">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="jobcastNotiApp" >
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>

            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body mt-50">
        <form onsubmit="return false">
            <div class="row gy-2">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5 class="mb-1">서비스 이용에 관한 기본적인 알림은 전송됩니다.</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-2">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary me-1 waves-effect waves-float waves-light">Save changes</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>